assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: MK Seiko Co., Ltd. develops, produces, and sells automotive service and information equipment, and household products. It offers car washing machines, car tire air filling machines, automatic car cleaning machines, car mat washers, fluid and oil related equipment, air conditioner related equipment, kerosene delivery lorries, pumps, and coolant cleaning machines, as well as LED display for gas stations, stores, construction, public demand information boards, and digital signages. The company also provides food temperature control cabinets; desktop filing machines; and stirring-related equipment, as well as cooking appliances, storage cabinets, and home appliances. MK Seiko Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1956 and is headquartered in Chikuma, Japan.
